            "text_size": "40,15",
            "txt_align": "start",
            "sub_heading": "",
            "heading": "",
            "text": "<h2>Smart Storage Tips<br/><br/></h2><h4>✅ Fold Neatly</h4><p>Use the classic square fold technique and <strong>refold every 2–3 months</strong> to prevent permanent creases.</p><h4>✅ Use Muslin Cloth Wraps</h4><p>Avoid plastic covers. Instead, wrap your saree in <strong>muslin or pure cotton</strong> fabric to allow it to breathe.</p><h4>✅ Separate Light & Dark Colors</h4><p>Store lighter shades separately to avoid color transfer or yellowing.</p>",
